    <article class="island visa-virtual-carousel">
        <h2 class="island--title">Visa<sup>®</sup> Virtual Account Benefits</h2>
        <div id="visa-virtual" class="carousel carousel-default  slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="5000">
            <!-- Indicators -->
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#visa-virtual" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#visa-virtual" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#visa-virtual" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>

            <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="item active">
                    <div class="plate plate-white plate-icon-red plate-size-double">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="i i--purchases">
                            <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#i--purchases"></use>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="i--plus">+</span>
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="i i--bills">
                            <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#i--bills"></use>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="item--title">Purchase or Payments Online, by Mail or Phone</h3>
                    <p class="item--text">You can use the Boss Revolution Visa Virtual Account to shop or pay your bills online, by mail or over the phone - everywhere Visa debit cards are accepted in the United States and District of Columbia. You can even use it to recharge your Boss Revolution account online or over the phone</p>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <div class="plate plate-white plate-icon-red">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="i i--gift">
                            <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#i--gift"></use>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="item--title">It’s also a perfect gift</h3>
                    <p class="item--text">Take the guesswork out of finding the right gift. Let family and friends use the Boss Revolution Visa® Virtual Account you send them to buy what they really want - and they’ll know that it came from you. <br />
                       Did you wait until the last minute? We’ll deliver the account information electronically to the recipient, making the Boss Revolution Visa Virtual Account the perfect last minute gift.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <div class="plate plate-white plate-icon-red">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="i i--secure">
                            <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#i--secure"></use>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="item--title">It’s Secure</h3>
                    <p class="item--text">The account must be registered by the recipient prior to use. It only takes a few minutes to register and get all the account information electronically. For your protection, a link will be sent in the confirmation SMS and email to a secure registration page. Once registered, the account is ready for immediate use.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

