    <article class="island">
        <h2 class="island--title">How It Work</h2>
        <section class="how-works how-works-4-blocks how-works-number-centered">
            <div class="how-works--block">
                <h3>Purchase a non-reloadable Visa Virtual Account at a Boss Revolution retailer</h3>
                <p>There is a $1.95 one-time load fee. There are no other transaction fees on the account.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-works--block">
                <h3>Provide your information and the recipient information to the retailer</h3>
                <p>Provide mobile number, email address.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-works--block">
                <h3>Specify the account balance</h3>
                <p>You can load the account with any amount between $20 and $200.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-works--block">
                <h3>The account information will be delivered to the recipient electronically</h3>
                <p>An SMS and email will be sent to the recipient to tell them how to register.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </article>

